| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5261 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 035da179-78e5-5039-a2d1-4e23f1a1b62a"
